{"tid":128122,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"咁樣叫唔叫上左煙癮","createTime":"2017-02-20T14:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T13:07:53.000Z","uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"efa0962d9e40de6b913f3c5a688f96edb2be2252","tid":128122,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:29:57.000Z","msg":"近排好多野煩<br />\n<br />\n有一日真係好大壓力，本身諗住食一枝睇下點<br />\n<br />\n點知佢未打火前聞落幾香，食落就無乜感覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後尾諗住唔理包煙。 <br />\n<br />\n點知每晚番屋企，啲憂愁壓力就湧上黎咁，途中忍唔住食一兩支，<br />\n<br />\n三日夾埋食左6支 ，算唔算上左癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8b1a48c85708abb1ec99c5ea03f23b76a42fb9","tid":128122,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f82cb7d9bef634d0fa69fe458609e9671d5d046","tid":128122,"uid":28059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:37:43.000Z","msg":"一概都是概率"},{"pid":"b9b4ab360f9bb694c84096f8f2f9f8736b393f3b","tid":128122,"uid":38573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:37:48.000Z","msg":"一日一包叫咩"},{"pid":"b4ca6a0bddaf779aa7c555f63bf531330952961f","tid":128122,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:38:09.000Z","msg":"好吸唔吸走去吸真煙<br />\n<br />\n你都係貪嗰種感覺啫<br />\n<br />\n食電子煙啦"},{"pid":"798dafe185498ff20823be62234932900d20ca91","tid":128122,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:52:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f69118ffdd31d06748e7caa055655a110ac5478","tid":128122,"uid":36829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:23:33.000Z","msg":"搞笑咩，我一日一包都未覺得自己上左癮la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96707daed7b966799611228d588550ffc36daa05","tid":128122,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s